
The clinical evaluation system for therapeutic effects of zzso which focuses on survival period and tumor response rate, has been proved not very proper for evaluating the therapeutic effects of traditional Chinese medicine zzso Quality of life zzso has been introduced into the effective evaluation system of zzso and zzso medicine because of its similarity in concept and extension with zzso at theory basis, syndrome zzso and evaluation of therapeutic zzso But there are no zzso questionnaires which can evaluate the therapeutic effects of zzso and zzso medicine zzso This article discussed the necessity and significance of developing zzso questionnaire special for zzso 

